'''杰梅恩·彭南特'''（{{lang-en|'''Jermaine Pennant'''}}，{{bd|1983年|1月15日|catIdx=Pennant, Jermain}}），出生於[[英格兰|英格兰]][[諾定咸|諾定咸]]，司職[[中場|翼鋒]]。现效力于[[新加坡职业足球联赛|新加坡职业足球联赛]]球队[[淡濱尼流浪足球會|淡濱尼流浪]]。他在2009年夏天與[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]解約，並加盟[[西甲|西甲]]剛季升級球會[[皇家薩拉戈薩|薩拉戈薩]]，於短暫借用到[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]後，由於表現出色，在2011年[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開後正式加盟。

==生平==
===球會===
賓納是[[諾士郡|諾士郡]]的青訓球員，是一名出波型右翼。1999年他以16岁之齢轉会至[[英超|英超]]球會[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]（[[轉會費|轉會費]]為250萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]），首次聯賽上陣對[[修咸頓|修咸頓]]便[[連中三元|連中三元]]，但六年間先後被外借到[[屈福特|屈福特]]、[[列斯聯|列斯聯]]、[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]各兩次。2005年正式被[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]收購。一季後被老牌球會[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]以670萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]（但根據[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]與[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]的協議，[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]要將這筆共以670萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的轉會費中的25%，即167.5万[[英鎊|英鎊]]給予[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]）將賓納特帶到[[晏菲路球場|晏菲路球場]]效力。加盟僅一季已成為利物浦的重要球員，並於對[[車路士|車路士]]的聯賽中入了一球精彩遠射。

2008/09年球季賓納上陣的次數大減，於2009年1月20日被外借到[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]直到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news | title =Portsmouth sign Pennant on loan | url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/7833429.stm | accessdate =2009-01-21 | publisher =[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date =2009-01-20 | archive-date =2020-11-09 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/7833429.stm | dead-url =no }}</ref></small>。季後遭利物浦棄用，於2009年7月9日離開[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]加盟[[西甲|西班牙]]球會[[皇家薩拉戈薩|薩拉戈薩]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/8143493.stm |title=Pennant signs for Real Zaragoza |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-09 |accessdate=2009-07-10 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303063510/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/8143493.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，球隊整季在聯賽榜下游掙扎，他在操練時需要翻譯才明白教練的指示，更因兩週三次遲到而被送回家<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1253549/Jermaine-Pennant-sent-home-Real-Zaragoza-late-weeks.html |title=Errant Jermaine Pennant sent home by Real Zaragoza for third late show in two weeks |publisher=''dailymail.co.uk'' |date=2010-02-25 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125232453/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1253549/Jermaine-Pennant-sent-home-Real-Zaragoza-late-weeks.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前，賓納獲借用返回[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]的[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]直到翌年1月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8957431.stm |title=Eidur Gudjohnsen among four new signings for Stoke |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-01 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303063531/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/8957431.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間表現出色，賓納表示希望繼續留效<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9181012.stm |title=Jermaine Pennant eyes permanent deal at Stoke City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-15 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2020-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303063532/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9181012.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但領隊[[東尼·佩利斯|東尼·佩利斯]]認為薩拉戈薩的600萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]開價過高<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9272838.stm |title=Tony Pulis rules out £6m Jermaine Pennant Stoke bid |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-09 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307194116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9272838.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，12月29日最終雙方達成協議，以170萬英鎊成交，金額可增加至280萬英鎊，賓納簽署兩年半合約正式加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9326671.stm |title=Stoke sign winger Jermaine Pennant on a permanent deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-29 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327124855/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9326671.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年10月12日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]向[[英超|英超]][[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]借用賓納，為期三個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19924304 |title=Wolves sign winger Jermaine Pennant from Stoke City on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-10-12 |accessdate=2013-06-29 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017021947/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19924304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年6月6日，[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]宣佈有7名球員不獲新合約可自由轉會，賓納為其中之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22798467 |title=Stoke City: Jermaine Pennant is one of seven players released |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-06-06 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927050210/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22798467 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.stokecityfc.com/news/article/potters-announce-retained-list-856356.aspx |title=Club confirm a number of departures following end of 2012/13 |publisher=''Stock City FC'' |date=2013-06-06 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906155640/https://www.stokecityfc.com/news/article/potters-announce-retained-list-856356.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年6月18日，賓納被放棄後12天，新任[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]領隊[[馬克·曉士|馬克·曉士]]重簽賓納，合約為期一年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22958716 |title=Jermaine Pennant re-signs for Stoke City on one-year deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-06-18 |accessdate=2013-06-29 |archive-date=2013-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131229045922/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22958716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
雖然賓納很早就展開其足球生涯，不過就从未入選過[[英格兰国家足球隊|英格兰国家足球隊]]，只曾在[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭青年軍]]效力。當發現其[[祖父|祖父]]是[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]人後，賓納於2011年3月主動接觸[[愛爾蘭足球協會|愛爾蘭足球協會]]關於他入選[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭國家隊]]的可能性<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9417873.stm |title=Stoke's Jermaine Pennant wants Republic of Ireland call |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-08 |accessdate=2011-03-08 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327124853/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/9417873.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==醉駕入獄==
2005年1月23日賓納將他的[[梅塞德斯-朋馳|-{zh-hans:奔驰;zh-hk:平治;zh-tw:朋馳;}-]]座駕在[[艾爾斯伯里|艾爾斯伯里]]撞上燈柱後被拘捕及控告醉酒駕駛及沒有[[保險|保險]]，而當時他仍在罰停駕駛的16個月期間。於3月1日被判罪名成立及入獄90日<small><ref>{{cite news | title =Jail for drink-driving footballer | url =http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/london/4307427.stm | accessdate =2009-01-21 | publisher =[[BBC|BBC]] news | date =2005-03-01 | archive-date =2007-01-09 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070109142315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/london/4307427.stm | dead-url =no }}</ref></small>。入獄30日後獲准[[假釋|假釋]]，賓納隨即返回[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]繼續披甲，但在假釋期間就算上場比賽仍需帶上電子監察器。

